{"tid":1645313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 民陣幾時再出嚟搞遊行","createTime":"2019-10-11T00:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T00:56:26.000Z","uid":5439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6340a00b28263b7c7192c2afc54207a3ea9ee38d","tid":1645313,"uid":5439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"我知依家攞張不反對通知書難過登天，但係唔代表難就唔去做。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日大家都休息，接收咗好多令人嘩然嘅新聞。喺時候比勇武知香港人其實未忘記！我哋唔可以停落嚟！<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好多和理非都等緊一個所謂合法嘅遊行，比勇武屌都好，佢哋都擺脫唔到做「非法」嘅嘢。（當然我唔認同遊行集會要有咁多限制）"},{"pid":"bc9ec6f0d7d739cf76f21035cdd840d892cdaee9","tid":1645313,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:16:40.000Z","msg":"民陣第十萬次請願~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efff2b86f88eda06adb74e024057e9fd41d41f4f","tid":1645313,"uid":108571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:17:09.000Z","msg":"個問題係佢申請唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbcda4b020d0b75927c6fef0f7d3abaea4d1b58","tid":1645313,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"抗議黑警，黨鐵害死香港人！"},{"pid":"a919f7442ceecf333d434815c4e64b61a68a3c82","tid":1645313,"uid":258133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OuLYtFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOuLYtFT.jpg&h=509483cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bc2152c87381083ceb39672e5bc81648362c0f6","tid":1645313,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"睇左未<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/you-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fyou-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqfzvTpW%2B